kubernates is container orchistrestion platform where me manae containers automatically generally kubernates is more relavent in tearm of using microservices..
their are diffrent components in kubernates which we have to look at 

###Master node
1) etdc-its database in master node which takes notes of all activity
2) api- its component of database where all actity  goes on
3) sheduler- sheduler is look at which resourses are free and according to them it sheduled over their 
4) controller- controller having overview of its child nodes pods and container

###child node components
1)kubelet-it is thing which connects child node and master node
2)kubeproxy- its thing which controlling the networking activities over the nodes between master child and all other 

